dct_title_s: Gray's Atlas Map of New York.

dct_description_sm: Prime meridians: Greenwich, Washington.  Includes inset maps of : Albany, Troy, Vicinity of New York, Oswego, Buffalo, Rochester, and Syracuse.  Includes on verso : Gray's atlas map of New York City, and Gray's atlas map of Connecticut with portions of New York & Rhode Island. Dimensions: 42 x 61 centimeters
